OL,3,GOPINIONCEscalating industrial relations
OL,4,Ctroubles for STV
OL,5,
OL,6,FIf you thought things could not get any
OL,7,Fworse for STV then you were wrong.
OL,9,FThe two main TV unions ` the National
OL,10,FUnion of Journalists and Bectu ` are to
OL,11,Fhold ballots on a pay strike.
OL,13,FThe company plans to freeze pay.
OL,15,FOf course a pay freeze actually means a
OL,16,Fpay cut after inflation is included.
OL,17,FInflation is currently at 3pc.
OL,19,FA pay freeze is never good news. It is
OL,20,Foften a sign of a company going through
OL,21,Fturbulent times.
OL,23,EPub: 22-Feb-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
