OL,3,GOPINIONCEscalating industrial relations
OL,4,Ctroubles for STV
OL,5,
OL,6,FBut this pay freeze follows on from big
OL,7,Fjob cuts linked to the planned cuts in
OL,8,Fnews programmes.
OL,10,FStaff who haven't taken redundancy have
OL,11,Fbeen told their pay will be cut in real
OL,12,Fterms.
OL,14,FEven if this is necessary to steady the
OL,15,Fship, it will hardly help staff loyalty
OL,16,Fand morale.
OL,23,EPub: 22-Feb-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
