OL,3,GOPINIONCEscalating industrial relations
OL,4,Ctroubles for STV
OL,5,
OL,6,FIt should be remembered that many jobs
OL,7,Fin television ` especially at the lower
OL,8,Flevels ` are not well paid. This is
OL,9,Ftrue across the industry and STV is
OL,10,Fprobably no more guilty of this than
OL,11,Fanyone else.
OL,13,FThose who can put up with modest pay or
OL,14,Fshort-term contracts in the early
OL,15,Fstages of their careers and survive
OL,16,Foften work their way up to jobs which
OL,17,Fare much more lucrative. Others bail
OL,18,Fout.
OL,23,EPub: 22-Feb-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
