OL,3,GOPINIONCEscalating industrial relations
OL,4,Ctroubles for STV
OL,5,
OL,6,FA pay freeze though can only make
OL,7,Fthings worse for everyone. It would
OL,8,Fhardly be a surprise if some loyal
OL,9,Fstaff find themselves wondering if
OL,10,Fthey'd be better off doing something
OL,11,Felse.
OL,13,FBut what is STV to do?
OL,15,FAdvertising revenue is down. The share
OL,16,Fprice collapsed last summer.
OL,18,FOfcom is expected to say whether the
OL,19,Fcuts to news will be allowed by the end
OL,20,Fof March.
OL,23,EPub: 22-Feb-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
