OL,3,GOPINIONCEscalating industrial relations
OL,4,Ctroubles for STV
OL,5,
OL,6,FThat's also when strikes on pay might
OL,7,Fbegin ` assuming the company doesn't
OL,8,Fcompromise.
OL,10,FFurther strike action by the NUJ linked
OL,11,Fto the job cuts is also possible though
OL,12,Fthe BBC reports that only a few staff
OL,13,Fare still at risk of compulsory
OL,14,Fredundancy.
OL,16,FIf the NUJ goes on strike again, it
OL,17,Fseems likely news will be blacked out.
OL,18,FJust like it was in January and during
OL,19,Fanother strike two years ago.
