OL,3,GOPINIONCEscalating industrial relations
OL,4,Ctroubles for STV
OL,5,
OL,6,FWhat about a Bectu strike though? Are
OL,7,Fits members responsible for STV
OL,8,Fplayout? If they are, this could prove
OL,9,Fsignificant. Do emergency playout plans
OL,10,Finclude provision for strikes?
OL,12,FAnd if STV compromises on pay ` as
OL,13,Fsurely it will have to at some point `
OL,14,Fwill this mean other cuts to pay for
OL,15,Fthe increased wage bill?
OL,17,FIt's all a very sad state of affairs
OL,18,Ffor staff, unions and a company which
OL,19,Fis still much loved in Scotland.
OL,23,EPub: 22-Feb-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
